                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The 120 total energy drained from a Magnetic proc is reduced to 30 energy."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Rapid Resilience",
                  "pageId": 573823,
                  "revisionId": 2720791,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "A Magnetic proc on Tenno normally lasts 3 seconds. With Rapid Resilience this is reduced to 0.75 seconds, because the energy drain has no delay it is not completely nullified."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Rapid Resilience",
                  "pageId": 573823,
                  "revisionId": 2720791,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The UI distortion effect is also reduced to 0.75 seconds."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Rapid Resilience",
                  "pageId": 573823,
                  "revisionId": 2720791,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Blast procs will deal damage after a delay of 0.37 seconds."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "source": "local-wiki-sqlite",
                  "pageTitle": "Rapid Resilience",
                  "pageId": 573823,
                  "revisionId": 2720791,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "A shield gate duration of more than 1 second will block all damaging status effects from damaging your health, except for Toxin , and during the shield gate invulnerability."
                }
              }
